-kong-police-beginning-11-aug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsend-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=1fa255cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/send-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug</a><br />\n<br />\n香港政府及警察策動831太子恐怖襲擊，請美國予以制裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=23291569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831</a><br />\n-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests"},{"pid":"03f2c26dfeecb312249b656d158ec9392c85d7b2","tid":1554943,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9896437504afe3bad484543b71f846ada3b63db6","tid":1554943,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"1f07d0fb9e21ff703da476d970ded53168ea0224","tid":1554943,"uid":248091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7a6de0522db4c4db55432b0055a6a41f5fbd2c1","tid":1554943,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新屋嶺附近就係專處理無名屍嘅沙嶺公墓！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n沙嶺公墓，是一個政府專為無人認領屍體而設的墳場。梁梓敦與食環署職員先帶領團友到棺木段，只見眼前盡是一片青蔥草綠的山頭，一塊又一塊小石碑歪歪斜斜的插在泥土中。冰冷的灰色<br />\n新屋嶺附近，係沙嶺墳場！<br />\n<br />\n石塊上，沒有名字，也沒有遺照，只有一組號碼，代表死亡年份及下葬的次序，連先人是男是女亦無從得知。<br />\n<br />\n相比殯儀館內繁複的儀式，這裏的身後事簡單得多，也落寞得多。葉先生補充，這裏每年只有約10具遺體被人認領，若七年內有家屬認領遺體，選擇重新安葬或留在原地，政府亦需向他們收回殮葬費。在沙嶺公墓，只有冷冰冰的程序，沒有一點多餘的關懷。<br />\n<br />\n食環署規定，凡於棺木段安葬七年的遺體，必須「起骨」火葬，並安放到另一山頭的骨灰區，同一個年份去世的先人，合葬在同一墓穴裏。數以百計同年逝世的「無主骨灰」，會一起撒落在一塊面積約兩呎乘兩呎的公墓下，上面只豎着一塊寫着年份的石碑，「所以家屬想認領遺體，一定要喺遺體仲放喺棺木段嘅時候認領，如果唔係，嚟到骨灰區就冇辦法了」。<br />\n<br />\n一年有幾百死者冇人理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/16931/%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93%E5%A2%B3%E9%81%8A-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%A4%E9%AD%82%E5%8C%96%E4%BD%9C%E7%84%A1%E6%83%85%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%90%88%E8%91%AC%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F16931%2F%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A2%2593%25E5%25A2%25B3%25E9%2581%258A-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E9%25AD%2582%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2591%25AC%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%259F&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=6fa70602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/16931/%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93%E5%A2%B3%E9%81%8A-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%A4%E9%AD%82%E5%8C%96%E4%BD%9C%E7%84%A1%E6%83%85%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%90%88%E8%91%AC%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%9F</a><br />\n【生死教育】沙嶺公墓墳遊 無名孤魂化作無情號碼合葬黃土"}]}